channel.title: My Third Duke of Edinburgh Site
channel.description: Recent content on My Third Duke of Edinburgh Site

item.title: April Update
item.description: I am increasingly getting better at running, however shortly after the last recorded run my parents became ill with a non-covid related illness and I have not been able to run. Despite this my bouldering and parkour sessions have started again which is good.

item.title: New Site
item.description: This details the first 5 run/rows of mine since I made the my 3dofe website. I struggled to keep my self motivated and still now. That being said, I always feel better for having done a run and will continue after dofe is over.
